msgid ""
"Dhcpd configuration settings are taken from the DHCP mini-HOWTO, which can "
"be found <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.tldp.org/HOWTO/DHCP/index.html\">here</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Dhcpd 설정 값은 DHCP 미니-하우투에서 취해졌고, 그것은 <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.tldp.org/HOWTO/DHCP/index.html\">여기</ulink>에서 찾을 수 있습니다."

